<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When try to set enconding on object construct the setEncoding is incorrect set as Array.</p>

<p>{panel:title=Line 60}
if (array_key_exists('encoding', $options)) {
    $this-&gt;setEncoding($options);
}
{panel}
Making Zend_Filter_StringToUpper::setEnconding() / Zend_Filter_StringToLower::setEnconding() to throws Zend_Filter_Exception "The given encoding 'array' is not supported by mbstring")</p>

<p>{panel:title=Correction}
if (array_key_exists('encoding', $options)) {
    $this-&gt;setEncoding($options['encoding']);
}
{panel}</p>

